      • getAbundanceExtremaInRange

        protected uk.co.strangeskies.mathematics.Range<Double> getAbundanceExtremaInRange(uk.co.strangeskies.mathematics.Range<Double> massRange)
        Find the range of abundances present within this range for this spectra.
        Parameters:
        massRange - the range between which to check for extrema.
        Returns:
        the range between the maxima and minima as approximated by any samples within the range given, null if there are no such samples.
